<item>
            <title>[LU-7969] No email received for comment on watched issue</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7969</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I did not receive an email when a comment was added to an issue I&apos;m a watcher on.  The comment was added at least several hours after I became a watcher.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7951&quot; title=&quot;NULL pointer dereference in vvp_io_write_start&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7951&quot;&gt;LU-7951&lt;/a&gt;   NULL pointer dereference on vvp_io_write_start&lt;br/&gt;
